author: cbc
title: RNC request assistance in locating missing 22-year-old woman
text:
The Royal Newfoundland Constabulary is asking for the public's help in finding a missing woman on the northeast Avalon.
Natalie Sinik, 22, was last heard from on Saturday, and is described as five-feet, six-inches tall, with a slim build, black hair and brown eyes. Police said no description of clothing was available.
Police say Sinik is believed to be in the company of 32-year-old Matthew Cooper. (Facebook)
Sinik is believed to be in the company of 32-year-old Matthew Cooper. He is described as six-feet tall, 160 pounds with brown hair and green eyes.
Anyone with information is asked to contact local police or the Royal Newfoundland Constabulary.
